title: AMERICAN HORROR STORIES Episode 7 Breakdown, Easter Eggs & Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment:

I still don’t understand why Scarlett only comes on the one day ruby can leave..she can literally come any other day of the year and get in the bath with her but on the day she can LEAVE we get in the tub..huh?
I’d rather eat a leather belt then watch teenagers bang or take a bath ever again 🤡
Just put Murder House to rest and give us more adult horror centric episodes like episodes 5-6 in season 2

Very conflicted on this one- I think I prefer American horror stories to not connect to too much of the other seasons- the strongest episodes in concept were rabbit rabbit- the infertility episode & the hills have eyes type episode - didn’t love then messing with the murder house lore because it was pretty perfect as it stood
